## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and publications up to October 2023. Some sources may not reflect the most recent scientific research or policy developments. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems means that predictions and models are subject to uncertainties. The report focuses on broad environmental impacts and may not cover all regional or localized effects of global warming.

